{"tid":2440392,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「面試100%合格的臉孔」李昇基、朴寶英拿下冠軍，男女前三名都好有說服力！","createTime":"2021-03-10T02:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T02:46:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31cf7862f0ee1dda58818fe4e3475c9e690baad7","tid":2440392,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:20:16.000Z","msg":"冠軍真的是實至名歸，關於「面試100%合格的臉孔」大家心中有名單嗎？<br />\n<br />\n在即將畢業之際，相信許多人都為了將來的工作出入而煩惱，而韓國網友也選出了他們認為面試官會喜歡的面孔，這些藝人光是看臉就讓人忍不住大喊一聲：「你合格了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此調查是韓國綜合教育機構Eduwill (에듀윌)向準備就業的1765人中票選而出。<br />\n<br />\n【男生組】<br />\n<br />\n冠軍：李昇基（32.3%）<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_286e6c206a20a701158a897f6bd63f9c/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-09/134149-899438.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_286e6c206a20a701158a897f6bd63f9c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-09%2F134149-899438.jpg&h=507f592b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二名：朴寶劍（31.4%）<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2ad35371d477c6530edfd7499dfefeda/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-09/134149-899439.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2ad35371d477c6530edfd7499dfefeda%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-09%2F134149-899439.jpg&h=e183e7b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三名：朴敘俊（28.2%）<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_73331b08c62d0d3b3191d9f20db5fa10/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-09/134149-899440.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_73331b08c62d0d3b3191d9f20db5fa10%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-09%2F134149-899440.jpg&h=49373f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外上榜的還有：宋江、宋仲基、車銀優、金宣虎、鄭雨盛。<br />\n<br />\n【女生組】<br />\n<br />\n冠軍：朴寶英（35.8%）<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a21e51a48f02d792185f045fc98b8a5f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-09/134149-899441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a21e51a48f02d792185f045fc98b8a5f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-09%2F134149-899441.jpg&h=ac05a97e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二名：金世正（22.8%）<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d04a8dd276269bc66ab8778fc5e549d4/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-09/134149-899442.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d04a8dd276269bc66ab8778fc5e549d4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-09%2F134149-899442.jpg&h=632f7ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三名：金泰梨（20.6%）<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5398cc26b85a5e19d07f2ff96ac0f781/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-09/134149-899443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5398cc26b85a5e19d07f2ff96ac0f781%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-09%2F134149-899443.jpg&h=e8a51181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外上榜的還有：申世景、IU、韓志旼、李寶英、宋慧喬。"},{"pid":"201908c21b45d3233832fc367e8089ec694811fa","tid":2440392,"uid":119695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"面試100%fail的臉孔：樓主"},{"pid":"87b32b147eefbc005e82650df52e196a6e82a80d","tid":2440392,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201908c21b45d3233832fc367e8089ec694811fa","tid":2440392,"uid":119695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"面試100%fail的臉孔：樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:23:17.000Z","msg":"你又知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8a825e74c00eace4d089a28271f701f5657f34","tid":2440392,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201908c21b45d3233832fc367e8089ec694811fa","tid":2440392,"uid":119695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"面試100%fail的臉孔：樓主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:23:41.000Z","msg":"連面試資格都冇啦佢<img src=\"/as